---
title: Honey Mustard & Thyme Chicken with Roast Veggie Medley & Feta
description: A classic combination of honey and mustard never goes amiss. We love the way these flavours caramelise in the pan, giving a crispy, sticky finish. We’ve used chicken thigh because it packs a fantastic flavour, remains moist as it cooks and complements the bed of delicious roast veggies.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/chicken-veggie-feta-bake-b96d2299.jpg
